{"type": "article", "id": 24741, "title": "UFO牛奶瓶包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-31T06:53:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 131, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021637390ml65WkC4phMTGzL.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个牛奶瓶包装模拟了 UFO 吸走牛的场景，也有洗手液利用了同样的设计。塑料瓶盖是宇宙飞船的形状，通过银色增加未来感，而瓶身是圆锥形的，模拟了光束发散的形状，在瓶子中间画出了黑色的奶牛的图像和光点，似乎马上就要吸走牛了，很有故事。至少对于特别需要喝牛奶的儿童或青少年来说很有吸引力。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021637369YR0xh4tDN6cVClL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163737Vpwsrt3GJfC8BThc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163737emvr1aQobHgBXzGw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021637380kqa7JFed9bY8yzZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163738DyJK5nGkw0uItWOL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}